			<SecondaryPreamble>
				<EnactingText>
					<Para>
						<Text>In exercise of the powers conferred upon me by section 33 of the Police Act 1964<FootnoteRef Ref="f00001"/>, and after taking into consideration the representations made by the Police Advisory Board for England and Wales and the recommendations made by the Police Negotiating Board for the United Kingdom, and furnishing each of the said Boards with a draft of the Regulations in accordance with section 46(3) of that Act<FootnoteRef Ref="f00002"/> and section 2(1) of the Police Negotiating Board Act 1980<FootnoteRef Ref="f00003"/>, I hereby make the following Regulations:</Text>
					</Para>
				</EnactingText>
			</SecondaryPreamble>
